Description:
    Creates a Stimulus controller with automatic registration

Example:
    rails generate stimulus cart

    This will create:
        app/javascript/controllers/cart_controller.js
        
    And automatically:
        - Register it in app/javascript/stimulus.js
        - Add pin to config/importmap.rb

Usage Examples:
    rails g stimulus product_filter
    rails g stimulus image_gallery
    rails g stimulus dropdown 